            <div class="text9">
                <p>Artist: Patrycja Rozwora </p>
                <p>Title: <em>Family Album</em></p>
                <p>
                    Staring with describing photographs, then moving on to memories which are then embodied by the use of words.
                    Patrycja Rozwora created a family portrait through three generations of the women in her family. 
                    In these five short stories, Patrycja wants to show different ways of living shaped by the complexity of roles and relationships we take or get throughout our lives. 
